Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I walked ten thousand miles,ten thousands miles to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And every gasp of breath,I grabbed it just to find you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I climbed up every hill to get to you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wandered ancient lands to hold just you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And every single step of the way,I paid
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Every single night and day I searched for you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,OP-EN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Through sand storms and hazy dawns I reached for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.31,0:01:13.31,JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
